e: ￹`Ira~ `cingra~ `a~ `tayni~ `haw~? `Awaayho~.￺Has he come yet? No.￻他來了嗎？還沒有
￹`Ci~`wawa~ `cingra~ `haw~? `Awa~.￺Does she have children? No.￻他有孩子嗎？沒有
￹`Ano~ `sa~`awa~`ay~ `'i~￺The least number to be involved would be...￻至少，最少，最低限度
￹`Pala~`awa~`en~ `ko~ `epoc~ `no~ `pi~`pasowal~ `nira~.￺Make what he says nonsense.￻讓他的話變成無用
